line_1: All powerless fell the losel's shafts malign:
line_2: And claim'd alliaunce with the Sisters nine;

line_1: All powerless fell the losel's shafts malign:
line_2: The peerless paragon of wit divine.

line_1: All powerless fell the losel's shafts malign:
line_2: Vaunting that every foe should rue its tine.
